title: Couple With Heart Woman Woman Light Skin Tone
alsoKnownAs: Two women holding hands with a heart
description: Represents a romantic couple composed of two women, both with light skin tones. It signifies love, partnership, and romantic relationships.
apple_vendor_description: This specific couple emoji on Apple devices beautifully illustrates two women with light skin tones, their forms gently brought together by a prominent, glowing red heart. Apple's design language shines through with soft rounded edges and realistic lighting, creating a sense of warmth and intimacy, making it a powerful symbol of love, relationship, and unity between two women.
